-- Wekerle’s Difference Capital Names Jim Shaw and Fecan to Board
-- B y   D o u g   A l e x a n d e r
-- 2013-06-17T11:26:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-17/wekerle-s-difference-capital-names-jim-shaw-and-fecan-to-board.html
Difference Capital Financial Inc.,
the Canadian merchant bank founded by former GMP Capital Inc.
trader Michael Wekerle, named Jim Shaw and Ivan Fecan to its
board.  Shaw, vice chairman of  Shaw Communications Inc. (SJR/B) , and Fecan,
former chief executive officer of CTVglobemedia Inc., will be
appointed today at the company’s annual meeting, the 
Toronto-based firm said in a statement.  Difference Capital, which was founded in May 2012 to focus
on technology-oriented investments, also said it formed an
advisory board that includes former Ontario Premier David
Peterson.  Other advisory board members are  Jim Ryan , former co-CEO of
 Bwin.Party Digital Entertainment Plc (BPTY) , former federal politician
John Reynolds, former DundeeWealth executive Lorie Haber and
Mark Opzoomer, former CEO of Russian Internet search engine
operator Rambler Media Ltd.  To contact the reporter on this story:
